some like towards me to ask me for protection but 
and she was an attractive girl and like I said she

01:50.174 --> 02:12.267
was I think she had either a doctorate or some 
degree of psychology so she was a career woman I

01:50.174 --> 02:12.267
remember she had wore even one of those wool 
dresses so were popular in those days, a knobby

02:12.247 --> 02:23.689
kind of thing, textured school dress, expensive 
